| Category | Unit | Data Type | Group | Filterable | Sortable | Comparable |
|----------|------|-----------|-------|------------|----------|------------|
| Length Overall | m | numeric | dimensions | true | true | true |
| Length Waterline | m | numeric | dimensions | true | false | true |
| Beam | m | numeric | dimensions | true | false | true |
| Draft | m | numeric | dimensions | true | false | true |
| Displacement | kg | numeric | performance | true | true | true |
| Ballast | kg | numeric | performance | true | false | true |
| Sail Area Main | m² | numeric | sailplan | true | false | true |
| Sail Area Genoa | m² | numeric | sailplan | false | false | true |
| Sail Area Spinnaker | m² | numeric | sailplan | false | false | true |
| Rig Type | - | text | sailplan | true | false | true |
| Keel Type | - | text | hull | true | false | true |
| Hull Material | - | text | hull | true | false | true |
| Cabins | - | numeric | accommodation | true | false | true |
| Berths | - | numeric | accommodation | true | false | true |
| Heads | - | numeric | accommodation | true | false | true |
| Max Occupancy | - | numeric | accommodation | true | false | true |
| Engine HP | hp | numeric | technical | true | false | true |
| Engine Type | - | text | technical | false | false | true |
