## Design Inspiration

Top sailing yacht websites to emulate:
- **Nautor's Swan**: Clean, image-focused, elegant typography
- **Amel Yachts**: Minimalist, professional, French elegance
- **Beneteau/Jeanneau**: Modern, bright, accessible
- **X-Yachts**: Performance-oriented, sleek, dark accents

**Design System**:
- Color palette: White/off-white background, navy blue accents, light grays
- Typography: Sans-serif (Inter or similar) for UI; elegant serif (Playfair Display) for headings
- Spacing: Generous whitespace, grid-based layouts
- Images: Full-bleed hero images on detail pages, consistent aspect ratios
- Components: Card-based yacht listings, subtle shadows, rounded corners (8px)
- No clutter: focus on specs and photos

