## Risks & Mitigations (Updated)

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Scraping blocked or anti-bot | Medium | High | Use headless browser with human-like delays, rotate user agents, fallback to manual entry |
| Spec normalization inconsistent | Medium | Medium | Build robust mapping rules; manual review step before seed |
| Dynamic filter performance with joins | Low | Medium | Add GIN index on spec_values (using `jsonb` if we store value in JSONB instead) OR use separate numeric/text columns; cache `/api/spec-categories` |
| Frontend breaks when new spec_categories added | Low | High | Write defensive rendering: only show categories that are `is_filterable`/`is_comparable` as configured; never assume fixed set |
| Admin auth too weak | Low | Medium | Use NextAuth.js with credentials provider or simple API key; document changing keys |
| Vercel serverless timeout on complex queries | Low | Low | Keep page size small (pagination), optimize queries, use edge functions with proper connection pooling |

